      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. you mentioned the tradeoff between efficiency and equity... but looking at the actual environmental data, isn't the climate necessity part kind of a settled fact? like, if it's proven to cut emissions, doesn't that make it a 'must-do' regardless of the economic debate?",
      "source": "evaluator"
